jaca.android.tools
Class BatteryArtifact

java.lang.Object
  cartago.Artifact
      jaca.android.dev.JaCaArtifact
          jaca.android.dev.BroadcastReceiverArtifact
              jaca.android.tools.BatteryArtifact

public class BatteryArtifact
extends BroadcastReceiverArtifact

Artifact that provides information about the device battery.

#### Observable Properties #####

  • battery_level(Value). Value = int value indicating the current device charge [0-100]%
  • battery_healt(Value). Value = {"dead", "good"}
  • battery_status(Value). Value = {"ok", "low"}
